title: The Bots x Los Rakas - "Spaceshippin'" (OFFICIAL AUDIO STREAM)
description:
Download "Spaceshippin'" 

"Spaceshippin'" from The Bots and Los Rakas, is the fifth track on the Converse compilation CONS EP VOL. 1. The track was recorded at The Himalayas and Perfect Kiss Studios, both in Los Angeles, California.

Produced by: Justin Warfield and Yeti Beats 
Music by: The Bots
Lyrics by: The Bots and Los Rakas
Vocals by: The Bots and Los Rakas
